@baseUrl = http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/leave
@employeeThreeId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000014

@employeeThreeAuth = Basic employee.three@company.com:123456
@managerThreeLevel1Auth = Basic manager.three.l1@company.com:123456
@managerThreeLevel2Auth = Basic manager.three.l2@company.com:123456
@managerThreeLevel3Auth = Basic manager.three.l3@company.com:123456

# Setelah step 3.1 berhasil, copy ID dari response lalu paste di sini
@leaveRequestId = paste-created-id-here


### 3.1 - Create Business Draft - Three Approval Layers
POST {{baseUrl}}/LeaveRequests
Authorization: {{employeeThreeAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Reason": "Case 3 - Three layer approval, approve all",
  "Employee_ID": "{{employeeThreeId}}",
  "RequestDate": "2026-05-05T09:00:00Z"
}


### 3.2 - Read Created Data
GET {{baseUrl}}/LeaveRequests(ID='{{leaveRequestId}}',IsActiveEntity=true)?$expand=LeaveApprovals
Authorization: {{employeeThreeAuth}}


### 3.3 - Submit Leave Request
### Expected:
### Status = InProgress
### Step 1 = Pending, IsCurrent = true
### Step 2 = Waiting, IsCurrent = false
### Step 3 = Waiting, IsCurrent = false
POST {{baseUrl}}/LeaveRequests(ID='{{leaveRequestId}}',IsActiveEntity=true)/LeaveService.submit
Authorization: {{employeeThreeAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}


### 3.4 - Read After Submit
GET {{baseUrl}}/LeaveRequests(ID='{{leaveRequestId}}',IsActiveEntity=true)?$expand=LeaveApprovals
Authorization: {{employeeThreeAuth}}


### 3.5 - Level 1 Approve
### Expected:
### Step 1 = Approved
### Step 2 = Pending
### Step 3 = Waiting
### LeaveRequest.Status = InProgress
POST {{baseUrl}}/LeaveRequests(ID='{{leaveRequestId}}',IsActiveEntity=true)/LeaveService.approve
Authorization: {{managerThreeLevel1Auth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Comments": "Case 3 level 1 approved"
}


### 3.6 - Read After Level 1 Approve
GET {{baseUrl}}/LeaveRequests(ID='{{leaveRequestId}}',IsActiveEntity=true)?$expand=LeaveApprovals
Authorization: {{employeeThreeAuth}}


### 3.7 - Level 2 Approve
### Expected:
### Step 1 = Approved
### Step 2 = Approved
### Step 3 = Pending
### LeaveRequest.Status = InProgress
POST {{baseUrl}}/LeaveRequests(ID='{{leaveRequestId}}',IsActiveEntity=true)/LeaveService.approve
Authorization: {{managerThreeLevel2Auth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Comments": "Case 3 level 2 approved"
}


### 3.8 - Read After Level 2 Approve
GET {{baseUrl}}/LeaveRequests(ID='{{leaveRequestId}}',IsActiveEntity=true)?$expand=LeaveApprovals
Authorization: {{employeeThreeAuth}}


### 3.9 - Level 3 Approve
### Expected:
### Step 1 = Approved
### Step 2 = Approved
### Step 3 = Approved
### LeaveRequest.Status = Approved
### LeaveRequest.IsClosed = true
POST {{baseUrl}}/LeaveRequests(ID='{{leaveRequestId}}',IsActiveEntity=true)/LeaveService.approve
Authorization: {{managerThreeLevel3Auth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Comments": "Case 3 level 3 approved"
}


### 3.10 - Read Approved Leave Request
GET {{baseUrl}}/LeaveRequests(ID='{{leaveRequestId}}',IsActiveEntity=true)?$expand=LeaveApprovals
Authorization: {{employeeThreeAuth}}